# PURR package

![Cute Cat](data:image/png;base64,)

This package provides a set of Python tools. it allow to manage projects configuration, you can config yours architectures and frameworks, and use theses configuration to easely create new projects.

## Installation

```bash

```

## Configuration
```bash
    purr config
```

##init project
```bash
    purr init <project_name>
```
